Bugs
====

 * AMS should maintain agent state, not the agent itself

Kinds of Agents
===============

 * News feed monitor (RSS/Atom)
 * E-mail monitor (POP) or sender (SMTP)
 * Front-end to web service
 * Text messaging agent
 * Instant Messaging (IM)
 * Twitter
 * Google Calendar Agent
 * Exchange Server Agent
 * Apple iCal Agent
 * Personal Shopper Agent
 * Upcoming.org Agent
 * Travel Agent (airline schedules & reservations; hotel listings & reservations; ???)
 * Movie Listings
 * Movie Information (IMDb)
 * Conferences & Speakers
 * LinkedIn Agent (?)
 * Weather
 * Google Maps Agent
 * iTunes
 * iPhoto
 * flickr Agent
 * Picasa Agent
 * Sports scores & statistics
 * Automobile makes & models

